definitions.definition: Any one of the several stages of postembryonic development which an arthropod undergoes , between molts , before it reaches sexual maturity .
An arthropod at a specified one of these stages of development.

main_definition: Any one of the several stages of postembryonic development which an arthropod undergoes , between molts , before it reaches sexual maturity .
secondary_definitions: An arthropod at a specified one of these stages of development.
( by extension ) A stage in development.
